reviews.text: Milano's pizza is our family favorite we have ordered for years even before my boys were born.we live just the street, they are the best pizza sandwiches pasta Mexican you can't go wrong, my department at the hospital we are always ordering milano's pizza or sandwiches. We love milano's it's our family favorite....thank you milano's ‚ù§Ô∏è and also I get broccoli Crust for my pizza so good .

They make a pretty mean pie! Some nice less traditional choices. The Philly cheesesteak pizza was amazing.

Could do without the selection of Chick tracts, but it‚Äôs not like I had to take one either.

The food is absolutely incredible, testimony to why I‚Äôve been a customer for over 12 years. I moved March 1 of this year to the city. I got delivery a month or so ago. I tried to get delivery this past Wednesday, June 25 I think and I was told they no longer deliver here where I live but they did not explain why. I find it hard to believe short of somebody being killed, there‚Äôs a good reason to eliminate 49 residence because of something that presumably one person did. I say this because there are regular shootings in the city here;  makes me wonder how they can deliver anywhere in Niles. I also provided a $10 tip for delivery every time. I have no way to go pick up a pizza‚Ä¶üíî

Best pizza in the area.   I usually get pizza and bread sticks, they are delicious and fresh every time.  Got the cookie pizza and not much for it.  If you want a great cookie pizza, then go to the Pizza Ranch in Holland.  It's a little over an hour away but the best cookie pizza, even reheated at home.  That's Gold Jerry Gold!

Glad that I discovered this gem a few years ago!!
I've tried a variety from the menu and it is always, consistently freshly prepared & delicious!
Over the years, I have found my orders to always be accurate, delivery is always timely, and service is above and beyond professional & friendly! All of this combined, makes each and every experience enjoyable and something that I actually look forward to (not just the good food!) Thank you so much Milano's for such dependable & excellent service!
